<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Account Verification</title>
  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: auto;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #333;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff !important;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    a {
      color: #007bff;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>

    <p>You have been invited to join <strong>PDSL Ehat</strong>.</p>
    <p>Please click the button below to verify your email and set your password:</p>

    <a href="{{verifyLink}}" class="button">Verify Account</a>

    <p>If the button above doesn't work, please use the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="{{verifyLink}}">{{verifyLink}}</a></p>

    <p>This link is valid for 15 minutes. If on the web portal it says "expired" or "invalid," please go to <a
        href="{{webUrl}}">{{webUrl}}</a>, click "Forgot Password," enter your email, and submit. You will receive a new
      email with instructions.</p>


    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you did not create this account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>— {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>